title: Lori  Foster-A Perfect Storm
description: Spencer Lark already knows too many secrets about Arizona Storm...including the nightmare she survived and her resulting trust issues. But in order to expose a smuggling ring -- and continue avenging his own tragic past -- the bounty hunter reluctantly agrees to make Arizona a decoy. Yet nothing has equipped him for the hypnotic blend of fragility and bravery she demonstrates, or for the protective instincts she stirs within him. Arizona wants to reclaim her life, which means acting as bait to lure the enemy into a trap. Sure it's dangerous, especially with a partner as distractingly appealing as Spencer.
